# Project Standards

- Stack: React (Vite) frontend, Express backend, SQLite database.
- API base path: `/api`. Use proper HTTP status codes.
- Never commit secrets; use `.env` and document variables in `.env.example`.
- Ticket status changes MUST go through `statusMachine.js` — never update status directly in routes.
- Valid statuses: Open, In Progress, Resolved, Closed, Cancelled.
- Valid priorities: Low, Medium, High, Critical.
- All timestamps in ISO 8601 UTC strings.
- Prefer small, focused changes. Match existing file structure and naming.
